value.title: Body by burpees: Raleigh firefighter sets Guinness World Record in the gym
value.description: A Raleigh firefighter is an unofficial Guinness World Record holder, pending paperwork.
value.body:
Guinness World Record (Photo: MGN Images)
RALEIGH (
)  A Raleigh firefighter is an unofficial Guinness World Record holder, pending paperwork.
5,297. Thats how many burpees Nick Christopoulos said he did on Sunday in an un-air-conditioned gym.
- Advertisement -
It was as it sounds, awfulyeah.
His venture to hold the title started simply enough- for every call at his firehouse, hed do 100 burpees.

value.body:
"@Beautiful Zhejiang" Video Contest Ready To Launch
News provided by
Jul 15, 2020, 06:10 ET
Share this article
,
July 15, 2020
/PRNewswire/ -- Organized by Information Office of Zhejiang Provincial Government and Zhejiang International Channel (ZTV-World), "@Beautiful Zhejiang" Global Short Video Contest is now ready to launch. The contest is seeking short videos no longer than 5 minutes from both home and abroad to show the beautiful landscape, culture, and modernization of the province.
The poster of this contest
The award-winning works will be displayed across the world. Award-winners will automatically get premium membership of
Blueberry Video Bloggers' Alliance @Beautiful Zhejiang
, a platform for works exhibition and insight sharing, and be offered priority access to follow-up media events and plenty of resources.
